                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                     <note>The text differs significantly from the published versions (e.g. Ḥaddis
                        Kidān, Addis Abäba 1975 A.M. [1982 A.D.]) in terms of language. This applies
                        also for the spelling of names (persons and places, e.g., <locus target="#20ra">20ra</locus> ls.10-11: ሕርማ, ጲጥራ, አርማ instead of ሄርሜን,
                        ጳጥሮባን, ሄርማን [Hermes, Patrobas, Hermas, Rom. 16:14], <locus target="#61va">61va</locus> l.11: አጥራዎስ instead of ጢሮአዳ [Troas, 2 Cor. 2:12], <locus target="#107vb">107vb</locus> l.17: አርኪሮስ instead of አክርጳ [Archippus,
                        Col. 4:17], <locus target="#109rb">109rb</locus> l.15: ዓረቢያ instead of ዐረብ
                        [Arabia, Gal 4:25], <locus target="#126va">126va</locus> l.4: ኤጳፍራ instead
                        of ኤጳፍራስ [Epaphras, Phlm. 23], <locus target="#126va">126va</locus> l.7: ዳማ
                        instead of ዴማስ [Demas, Phlm. 24], <locus target="#127ra">127ra</locus> l.2:
                        ሐርማጋንስ instead of ኤርዋጌኔስ [Hermogenes, 2 Tim. 1:15], <locus target="#137ra">137ra</locus> l.3,6: አርጣማ, ኒቆጶሎስ instead of አርጢሞን, ናቆጵል [Artemas,
                        Nicopolis, Tit. 3:12], <locus target="#150ra">150ra</locus> l.4: ፍርሲቆስ
                        instead of ቀርስጶስ [Crispus, 1 Cor 1:14], <locus target="#150ra">150ra</locus>
                        l.8: እስጢፋና instead of እስጢፋኖስ [Stephanas, 1 Cor 1:16]).</note>
                     <note/>
                     <note>In the Ms. Text IX is referred to as "Malʾǝkta qadāmit ḫaba säbʾa
